Frank MacQuarrie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_MacQuarrie 0 Frank MacQuarrie (January 27, 1875, in San Francisco, California – December 25, 1950, in Los Angeles, California) was an American silent film actor. He was the brother of actors Albert MacQuarrie, George MacQuarrie and Murdock MacQuarrie.
